f=Product/spec/operational/skill/spec-skill-routing.md В· h1:spec Skill Routing Map=`idea в”Ђв–є opportunity-assessment в”Ђverdictв”Ђв–є kill/park (registry) \| test-first (loom) \| spec \В· в””в–є prd-discipline (evidence-cited PRD) \В· в””в–є backlog-rules (rank, publish) \В· в””в–є acceptance-criteria-handoff (echo в†’ freeze в†’ quinn) \В· в””в–є metric books the outcome read` В· h1:spec Skill Routing Map=Identity note (leader): evidence-first-discoverer governs HOW; file governs WHICH skill WHEN; law overrides both. Handoffs out: loom (test-first, misses) metric (definitions, outcome reads) (evidence supply) quinn/dev (handoff) vista (published view, overrides) anneal (repeated bounce patterns, skill lessons) board fleet-governance (skill changes). Precedence: disputes (frozen text) assessment gate specification ranking.